---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-iron-800 bg-iron-950/80 py-10 text-sm text-iron-400">
  <div class="container-wide grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
    <div>
      <div class="text-iron-100 font-semibold">OpenFront 情报站</div>
      <p class="mt-2 text-iron-400 leading-relaxed">围绕开源 RTS 游戏 OpenFront.io 整理的中文机制、数据与攻略资料库。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="text-iron-100 font-semibold">导航</div>
      <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
        <li><a class="nav-link" href={`${base}mechanics/`}>游戏机制</a></li>
        <li><a class="nav-link" href={`${base}database/`}>单位数据库</a></li>
        <li><a class="nav-link" href={`${base}strategies/`}>战术攻略</a></li>
        <li><a class="nav-link" href={`${base}changelog/`}>更新日志</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="text-iron-100 font-semibold">来源</div>
      <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
        <li><a class="nav-link" href="https://openfront.io/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">官方站点</a></li>
        <li><a class="nav-link" href="https://github.com/openfrontio/OpenFrontIO" rel="noopener" target="_blank">GitHub 源码</a></li>
        <li><a class="nav-link" href={`${base}about/`}>关于本站</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="text-iron-100 font-semibold">声明</div>
      <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed">本站为社区资料站，内容基于 AGPL-3.0 源码与 CC BY-SA 资源整理，非官方。OpenFront © OpenFront and Contributors。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-wide mt-8 flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-iron-800 pt-4 text-xs text-iron-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
    <span>© {year} OpenFront Intel · 数据采集自 OpenFrontIO v24</span>
    <span class="font-mono">made with Astro</span>
  </div>
</footer>
